      "subject": "How Acme’s new AI platform can boost lead conversion",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI saw Acme’s recent launch of the AI‑powered analytics platform – impressive work! We recently helped a SaaS company similar to yours increase lead conversion by 35% using our AI‑driven lead scoring solution. I thought the results might resonate with your new platform. Would you be open to a quick 15‑minute chat next week?\n\nBest,\n[Your Name]",
      "send_at": "2025-12-10T09:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "subject": "Thoughts on AI‑driven lead scoring for Acme?",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nJust following up on my previous email. With Acme’s focus on AI analytics, our case‑study on a 35% lift in lead conversion could be a great fit for your upcoming initiatives. Let me know if you’d like to see the detailed results.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]",
      "send_at": "2025-12-12T09:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "step": 3,
      "subject": "Final note – helping Acme achieve higher conversion rates",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI understand you’re busy, so I’ll keep this brief. Our SaaS client saw a 35% boost in qualified leads after implementing our solution alongside their AI platform. If you’re interested in exploring a similar impact at Acme, I’d love to schedule a call.\n\nThank you for considering,\n[Your Name]",
      "send_at": "2025-12-15T09:00:00Z"
    }
  ]
}
